single-tree.original-sentence: MobileMedia Corp was named in a class action shareholder lawsuit over alleged violations of securities laws, attorneys for the plaintiff said.
MobileMedia was not immediately available for comment.

The complaint, filed in the U.S. District Court of New Jersey, is on behalf of purchasers of the company's common stock between August 2, 1995 (corrects from 1996) and September 27, 1996, the plaintiff's lawyers said in a statement.
The complaint alleges that company executives failed to disclose the integration problems it has had with recent acquisitions, among other things.
